{"id": "42181", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=42181", "title": "Writhing Ingress", "text": "Writhing Ingress is a &lt;a href=\"Library%20of%20Zoltun%20Kulle\"&gt;Library of Zoltun Kulle&lt;/a&gt; zone in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\nAfter the conclusion of the &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Exile\"&gt;Dark Exile&lt;/a&gt;, Zoltun Kulle retired to his library to conduct his magical research. He tried to replicate the &lt;a href=\"soulstone\"&gt;soulstone&lt;/a&gt;s; summoning &lt;a href=\"demon\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt;s to seal in his prototypes. Unfortunately they were all failures and he was left with a surfeit of demonic remains.\nHe tried fashioning guardians from these remains. Sadly, the &lt;a href=\"Patchwork%20Maw\"&gt;resulting monsters&lt;/a&gt; were aggressive and unpredictable, costing him a number of his servants. He decided to lock the failed guardians and the other remains in a section of his library; separating them from the rest of the library with magical barriers.\nOver the years, the demonic parts have fused in unpredictable ways creating a &lt;a href=\"Aberration\"&gt;new breed of abominations&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn-game.\nIt is located west from &lt;a href=\"the%20Grand%20Vestibule\"&gt;the Grand Vestibule&lt;/a&gt;, and east from the &lt;a href=\"Well%20of%20Knowledge\"&gt;Well of Knowledge&lt;/a&gt;, effectively bridging the two zones. &lt;a href=\"The%20Terminus%20%28Diablo%20Immortal%29\"&gt;The Terminus&lt;/a&gt; is located here as a 'sub-zone'. It is isolated from the rest of the library by magical barriers.\nIt holds a &lt;a href=\"waypoint\"&gt;waypoint&lt;/a&gt;. Furthermore, if players use the &lt;a href=\"Ancient%20Passage\"&gt;Ancient Passage&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Bilefen\"&gt;Bilefen&lt;/a&gt;, it will deposit them in the Ingress."}
