{"id": "45920", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=45920", "title": "Yves", "text": "Yves is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; that is seen in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\".\nBiography.\nYves is a veteran &lt;a href=\"demon%20hunter\"&gt;demon hunter&lt;/a&gt;. Around &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231270\"&gt;1270&lt;/a&gt;, he was in &lt;a href=\"Shassar%20Sea\"&gt;Shassar Sea&lt;/a&gt; hunting &lt;a href=\"demon\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt;s he noticed that someone had been dissecting demon bodies. He enlisted the help of &lt;a href=\"the%20Shard-seeker\"&gt;a passing adventurer&lt;/a&gt; to investigate. At the end they found out that a &lt;a href=\"Tarhan%20the%20Ambitious\"&gt;Sand Scorpion bandit&lt;/a&gt; was invoking an ancient &lt;a href=\"Fahir\"&gt;Fahir&lt;/a&gt;ian ritual to gain immortality, and the demons were used as ritual components. After disrupting the ritual, the bandit was consumed as sacrifice and the demon parts were restored to life. With the help of the &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt; he was able to kill the demons.\nIn-game.\nYves gives the &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal%20Side%20Quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; \"&lt;a href=\"Unholy%20Ascension\"&gt;Unholy Ascension&lt;/a&gt;\". He can be found in front of the portal to the &lt;a href=\"Domain%20of%20Horror\"&gt;Domain of Horror&lt;/a&gt; within &lt;a href=\"Sereth%20Outpost\"&gt;Sereth Outpost&lt;/a&gt;. He can use &lt;a href=\"Multishot\"&gt;Multishot&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Rain%20of%20Vengeance%20%28Diablo%20Immortal%29\"&gt;Rain of Vengeance&lt;/a&gt;."}
