{"id": "51206", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=51206", "title": "Zabsi", "text": "Zabsi is a &lt;a href=\"Lilin\"&gt;Lilin&lt;/a&gt;, and one of the survivors of &lt;a href=\"Baal\"&gt;Baal&lt;/a&gt;'s rampage on the &lt;a href=\"Ancients%27%20Cradle\"&gt;Ancients' Cradle&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nAfter praying to &lt;a href=\"Lilith\"&gt;Lilith&lt;/a&gt; for a cure to their affliction didn't work, Zabsi and &lt;a href=\"Dradwyr\"&gt;Dradwyr&lt;/a&gt; went to &lt;a href=\"Shieldholm\"&gt;Shieldholm&lt;/a&gt; on his suggestion to pray to symbols of &lt;a href=\"Inarius\"&gt;Inarius&lt;/a&gt;. As Dradwyr began his prayer, there was a flash of light, and then he was gone.\nShortly after, &lt;a href=\"the%20Shard-seeker\"&gt;the outlander&lt;/a&gt; that saved the Cradle was passing by, and she begged their help to find Dradwyr. The outlander agreed, and they began their search. They were shortly attacked by &lt;a href=\"Sacred%20Guardian\"&gt;Sacred Guardian&lt;/a&gt;s, who Zabsi recognized as guards to the trial of &lt;a href=\"Purity%27s%20Penance\"&gt;Purity's Penance&lt;/a&gt;. The duo rushed to the Ritual Site, defeating more guardians along the way. There they found Dradwyr being put through Purity's Penance. Dradwyr survived the rite unscathed, to the annoyance of the &lt;a href=\"Sanctifier\"&gt;Sanctifier&lt;/a&gt;s who blamed her companion.\nIn-game.\nZabsi is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;.\" She is triggers the &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal%20Side%20Quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; \"\"."}
