{"id": "34935", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=34935", "title": "Zaven Haroutunian", "text": "Zaven Haroutunian was a senior game designer for \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". He began working at &lt;a href=\"Blizzard%20Entertainment\"&gt;Blizzard Entertainment&lt;/a&gt; in 2008, and began work on Diablo III in 2010. He is currently the lead dungeon designer for \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\"."}
