{"id": "43501", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=43501", "title": "Zepydra", "text": "Zepydra is an &lt;a href=\"angel\"&gt;angel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\".\nZepydra has a low opinion of &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt;s and their wont for violence, but is willing to work alongside them as need dictates.\nBiography.\nZepydra was part of a group of angel sentinels led by &lt;a href=\"Verathiel\"&gt;Verathiel&lt;/a&gt;. They discovered the &lt;a href=\"Realm%20of%20Damnation\"&gt;Realm of Damnation&lt;/a&gt; as it was taking shape. Cut off from the &lt;a href=\"High%20Heavens\"&gt;High Heavens&lt;/a&gt;, they carved out &lt;a href=\"the%20Last%20Vestige\"&gt;a foothold&lt;/a&gt; in the realm, battling &lt;a href=\"demon\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt;s over the eons.\nHorn of Harmony.\nSometime after &lt;a href=\"Skarn\"&gt;Skarn&lt;/a&gt;'s death, Zepydra heard the melody of an angelic horn as they roamed the Realm of Damnation. At the site they found &lt;a href=\"Kyrel\"&gt;Kyrel&lt;/a&gt;\u2014alongside a &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt;, battling demons. Zepydra joined the battle to help, and after the demons were killed, thanked the mortal for serving their purpose. Zepydra later returned to the Last Vestige.\nHellstorm.\nZepydra feared that a Hellish storm would overtake the Last Vestige. With the aid of a &lt;a href=\"Classes%23Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;hero/group of heroes&lt;/a&gt;, two standards were raised, conjuring a shield of light that would protect the holdfast.\nWaiting Doom.\nZephydra realized that three angels had gone missing. With the help of a &lt;a href=\"Class%23Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;hero/group of heroes&lt;/a&gt;, Zepydra ventured into the &lt;a href=\"Halls%20of%20Punishment\"&gt;Halls of Punishment&lt;/a&gt; to rescue them. The first angel they encountered was beyond saving, and with the second, they could not intervene due to \"the doom.\" They stayed with the second angel to break the curse, while they sent the hero(es) to retrieve the third angel. They returned with the second to find the hero(es) taking care of the last demons, and the third angel was saved as well. They and the angels headed back to regroup, while they told the mortal(s) that they would have need of each other again.\nIn-game.\nZepydra appears in the &lt;a href=\"Realm%20of%20Damnation\"&gt;Realm of Damnation&lt;/a&gt; zone in the \"&lt;a href=\"Hellstorm\"&gt;Hellstorm&lt;/a&gt;\" and \"&lt;a href=\"Waiting%20Doom\"&gt;Waiting Doom&lt;/a&gt;\" &lt;a href=\"side%20quest\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt;s.\nZepydra's gender is never specified; in quest text, terms such as \"them\" and \"they\" are always used."}
