{"id": "24677", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=24677", "title": "Beacon of Ytar", "text": "Beacon of Ytar is a\u00a0\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Passive%20skill%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;passive skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It is unlocked at level 35 and reduces &lt;a href=\"cooldown\"&gt;cooldown&lt;/a&gt;s of all skills.\nThe 20% benefit from this skill does not add with any other form of cooldown reduction (CDR). It can be calculated in a sequence with all other sources of CDR, with each one applying only to the cooldown length remaining after taking the previous reductions into account."}
