{"id": "15730", "revid": "13298744", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=15730", "title": "Beds", "text": "Beds are a type of unlabeled &lt;a href=\"Containers\"&gt;container&lt;/a&gt;. Unlike typical containers, floating the mouse over a bed will not reveal any name, indicating potential treasure might be located there.\nTo search a bed, just click on the blankets, they will flip up for a moment and loot may fly out onto the floor.\nBeds do not seem to have very good treasure, often only &lt;a href=\"Gold\"&gt;coins&lt;/a&gt; and/or &lt;a href=\"potions\"&gt;potions&lt;/a&gt;. Beds may also occasionally house a zombie or skeleton in it, which wakes up and attacks when the bed is searched."}
