{"id": "24816", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=24816", "title": "Black Hole", "text": "Black Hole is a Mastery skill that was introduced in \"&lt;a href=\"Reaper%20of%20Souls\"&gt;Reaper of Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nIn-game.\nBlack Hole pulls in all enemies in range (counts as &lt;a href=\"Knockback\"&gt;Knockback&lt;/a&gt;), briefly preventing them from all actions, and deals massive &lt;a href=\"damage%20over%20time\"&gt;damage over time&lt;/a&gt; in that area. It is a useful skill to use in conjunction with and/or &lt;a href=\"Strongarm%20Bracers\"&gt;Strongarm Bracers&lt;/a&gt;."}
