{"id": "8820", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8820", "title": "Black Razor", "text": "The Black Razor is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;Unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Swords\"&gt;Sword&lt;/a&gt; from \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20%28game%29\"&gt;Diablo I&lt;/a&gt;\" that is found randomly. Its very low damage almost nullifies the 150% bonus. That, and its mediocre abilities makes it a weapon only to be used for the first few stages of the game."}
