{"id": "41517", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=41517", "title": "Blackstone Village", "text": "Blackstone Village was a &lt;a href=\"town\"&gt;town&lt;/a&gt; in/near the &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Wood\"&gt;Dark Wood&lt;/a&gt;. \nLore.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231270\"&gt;1270&lt;/a&gt;, Blackstone was razed by the &lt;a href=\"Bloodsworn\"&gt;Bloodsworn&lt;/a&gt;, and seeded with &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Creeper\"&gt;Dark Creeper&lt;/a&gt;s and other strange plants. Practically every man, woman, and child in the village was slaughtered and their &lt;a href=\"blood\"&gt;blood&lt;/a&gt; collected. While the Bloodsworn believed they had killed everyone, there were a few survivors who managed to escape.\nAs &lt;a href=\"the%20Shard-seeker\"&gt;the Shard-seeker&lt;/a&gt; made their way through the village, they found a number of the villagers' bodies, all of which had been drained of their &lt;a href=\"blood\"&gt;blood&lt;/a&gt; by the vines. &lt;a href=\"Alyssa\"&gt;Alyssa&lt;/a&gt; was the only survivor they found, and even then, did not make it far out of the village before being killed herself.\nThe Bloodsworn remained in the ruins of Blackstone, even after the defeat of &lt;a href=\"the%20Countess\"&gt;the Countess&lt;/a&gt;. An unknown party posted a &lt;a href=\"bounty\"&gt;bounty&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Westmarch%20%28City%29\"&gt;Westmarch&lt;/a&gt;, requesting that &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt;s kill the Bloodsworn who had taken up residence, in order to avenge the fallen.\nThe survivors the Bloodsworn missed made it to &lt;a href=\"Eastgate%20Keep\"&gt;Eastgate Keep&lt;/a&gt;, where they swore revenge. The Bloodsworn were eventually wiped out, and &lt;a href=\"The%20Bloodsworn%20Hunter%20%28Character%29\"&gt;a lone hunter&lt;/a&gt;, a survivor of Blackstone, scoured &lt;a href=\"Khanduras\"&gt;Khanduras&lt;/a&gt; for any sign of them.\nIn-game.\nThe village is a zone of the Dark Wood in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". It is linked to the &lt;a href=\"Cairn-Crested%20Path\"&gt;Cairn-Crested Path&lt;/a&gt;, and is effectively the zone's starting area. It hosts a &lt;a href=\"waypoint\"&gt;waypoint&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "41516", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=41516", "title": "Blackstone Village (Quest)", "text": "Blackstone Village is the first &lt;a href=\"quest\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Wood\"&gt;Dark Wood&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". It triggers as soon as one enters the zone on their initial playthrough. Upon completion, it leads directly into \"&lt;a href=\"Lucian%27s%20Hope\"&gt;Lucian's Hope&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\n\"Somewhere in the Dark Wood, a &lt;a href=\"Worldstone\"&gt;Worldstone&lt;/a&gt; shard is already in &lt;a href=\"the%20Countess\"&gt;evil hands&lt;/a&gt;. Continue your journey and recover the shard before it is too late.\"\n\"A voice calling out for help has led you to the village of &lt;a href=\"Blackstone%20Village\"&gt;Blackstone&lt;/a&gt;. Aid the man before it is too late.\""}
