{"id": "52839", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=52839", "title": "Blade Beam", "text": "Blade Beam is a skill used by some &lt;a href=\"monster\"&gt;monster&lt;/a&gt;s in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". A &lt;a href=\"weapon\"&gt;weapon&lt;/a&gt; is required to use it. The monster charges their weapon before slashing, releasing waves of force in a straight line. Some monsters enhance the skill with &lt;a href=\"elemental%20damage\"&gt;elemental damage&lt;/a&gt;. It is used by &lt;a href=\"Maliduce\"&gt;Maliduce&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Defamer\"&gt;Defamer&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"%22Talva%20Silvertongue%22\"&gt;\"Talva Silvertongue\"&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"the%20Countess\"&gt;the Countess&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Zatham\"&gt;Zatham&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Zolthrax\"&gt;Zolthrax&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Shaddox\"&gt;Shaddox&lt;/a&gt;, Verathiel, &lt;a href=\"Lassal\"&gt;Lassal&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Vitaath\"&gt;Vitaath&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ophinneb\"&gt;Ophinneb&lt;/a&gt;."}
