{"id": "43287", "revid": "31719788", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=43287", "title": "Dravec", "text": "Dravec is a &lt;a href=\"boss\"&gt;boss&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\".\nBiography.\nDravec was an acolyte of the &lt;a href=\"Sanctified%20Earth%20Monastery\"&gt;Sanctified Earth Monastery&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Oza\"&gt;Oza&lt;/a&gt;. In &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231265\"&gt;1265&lt;/a&gt;, he lost his &lt;a href=\"Tayev\"&gt;younger brother&lt;/a&gt; at the fall of &lt;a href=\"Mount%20Arreat\"&gt;Arreat&lt;/a&gt; and became obsessed with finding a way to resurrect him. Sometime later, he made a pact with a &lt;a href=\"Skarn\"&gt;Skarn&lt;/a&gt; (who was in the guise as a God of Retribution). His &lt;a href=\"Vitalya\"&gt;master&lt;/a&gt; warned him against using the power of a Chaos God. \nIn &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231270\"&gt;1270&lt;/a&gt; with the emergence of the &lt;a href=\"Worldstone\"&gt;Worldstone&lt;/a&gt; shardss, Skarn promised Dravec to reunite him with his brother if he could bring a Worldstone shard to him. Dravec raided the Sanctified Earth Monastery in search of the Worldstone shard that was stored there, but couldn't find it, even after forcefully interrogating his master. In a fit of rage, he killed Vitalya.\nDravec was exiled from the &lt;a href=\"Veradani\"&gt;Veradani&lt;/a&gt; for that crime, and the &lt;a href=\"Patriarchs\"&gt;Patriarchs&lt;/a&gt; sent monks to hunt him down. Dravec fled Zavain for a time, but later returned, now allied with the &lt;a href=\"Cult%20of%20Damnation\"&gt;Cult of Damnation&lt;/a&gt;. The cult made a base in the abandoned &lt;a href=\"Zakarum\"&gt;Zakarum&lt;/a&gt; chapel within the &lt;a href=\"Misty%20Valley\"&gt;Misty Valley&lt;/a&gt;; as its residual &lt;a href=\"Light\"&gt;Light&lt;/a&gt; kept &lt;a href=\"Nightmare%20%28monster%29\"&gt;nightmares&lt;/a&gt; away. Meanwhile, Dravec laired in a cave within the Misty Valley. During this period, he learnt a lot of infernal lore and profane texts.\nAt the end it was all a trick. Instead of resurrecting Tayev, Skarn fused the brothers' &lt;a href=\"soul\"&gt;soul&lt;/a&gt;s together, creating a new &lt;a href=\"Twin%20Souls\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn-game.\nDravec is the major antagonist for the storyline quests of &lt;a href=\"Mount%20Zavain\"&gt;Mount Zavain&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Frozen%20Tundra\"&gt;Frozen Tundra&lt;/a&gt;. He is fought as a &lt;a href=\"boss\"&gt;boss&lt;/a&gt; via the &lt;a href=\"Twin%20Souls\"&gt;Twin Souls&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"monster\"&gt;monster&lt;/a&gt;, though is not a boss himself."}
