{"id": "26908", "revid": "25771421", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=26908", "title": "Eberli Charo", "text": "Eberli Charo is a\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Shields\"&gt;shield&lt;/a&gt; in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires\u00a0&lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt;\u00a031 to drop.\nThe special affix is invalidated with the Fires of Heaven rune of &lt;a href=\"Heaven%27s%20Fury\"&gt;Heaven's Fury&lt;/a&gt;. However, the shield was never designed to be used with that rune. It allows selection of more damage impacting rune selection (i.e. Ascendancy, Blessed Ground or Split Fury) in builds centering on Heaven's Fury. This is especially true when paired with &lt;a href=\"Fate%20of%20the%20Fell\"&gt;Fate of the Fell&lt;/a&gt;. \nDue to this affix, the shield is obviously &lt;a href=\"Crusader\"&gt;Crusader&lt;/a&gt;-oriented."}
