{"id": "43295", "revid": "52696024", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=43295", "title": "Echo of the Immortal", "text": "Echo of the Immortal is an event in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\".\nGameplay.\nThe event is held from August 17, 3:00 a.m. to September 14, 3:00 a.m' server time. It is available for players who are at least &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;level&lt;/a&gt; 40.\nEcho is similar to &lt;a href=\"Challenge%20of%20the%20Immortal\"&gt;Challenge of the Immortal&lt;/a&gt;. In it, 15 players face off against one randomly chosen player imbued with the power of &lt;a href=\"the%20Immortal\"&gt;the Immortal&lt;/a&gt;. If the group of players are victorious in besting the Immortal, the match becomes a free-for-all. To initiate the event, players must speak to the &lt;a href=\"Battleground%20Captain\"&gt;Battleground Captain&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Westmarch%20%28City%29\"&gt;Westmarch&lt;/a&gt;."}
