{"id": "10149", "revid": "2042971", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=10149", "title": "Elemental (Spell)", "text": "Elemental is a Fire spell in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20I\"&gt;Diablo I&lt;/a&gt;\".\nGeneral Information.\nWhen cast, this spell creates an elemental being in form of a humanoid figure of fire. The elemental will then quickly run towards the selected target and explode, hitting them for high Fire damage. Both damage and speed grow with Character and Spell Levels. It can hit a second foe (but only a total of two), if one is very close to the primary target.\nElemental is capable of hitting enemies around corners, pursues its prey if target moves, and if cast in an open space, it seeks out a target on its own, homing at the first foe it sees.\nIt does roughly half the damage of a , and only damages up to 2 targets, but can hit targets out of line of sight and homes at enemies. However, its high Mana cost and Magic requirements limit its usefulness.\nDamage Calculation:\nElemental splash damage is 1/64th of the total damage. It is applied each .05 seconds for .7 seconds (14 tries) and is not &lt;a href=\"block\"&gt;block&lt;/a&gt;able. Thus, as is the case with Fireball, the splash damage from an Elemental will deal damage even if the spell itself is blocked.\nRec stands for \"Recursive\" function."}
{"id": "24322", "revid": "26096179", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=24322", "title": "Elemental Arrow", "text": "Elemental Arrow\u00a0is\u00a0a\u00a0\u00a0Secondary skill in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It bears some resemblance to &lt;a href=\"Amazon\"&gt;Amazon&lt;/a&gt; skills like &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Arrow\"&gt;Fire Arrow&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Cold%20Arrow\"&gt;Cold Arrow&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Exploding%20Arrow\"&gt;Exploding Arrow&lt;/a&gt;,\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Ice%20Arrow\"&gt;Ice Arrow&lt;/a&gt;,\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Immolation%20Arrow\"&gt;Immolation Arrow&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0and\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Freezing%20Arrow\"&gt;Freezing Arrow&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn-game.\nFires a charged arrow that &lt;a href=\"piercing\"&gt;pierces&lt;/a&gt; through all enemies in its path (roughly 80 yards), hitting each for &lt;a href=\"Fire\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; damage. It counts as &lt;a href=\"missile\"&gt;missile&lt;/a&gt;, and cannot pierce through obstacles."}
